page.title: 01Queensbury
page.content: QUEENSBURY IS AN OLD VILLAGE ITS SUROUNDINGS ARE FIELDS,FACTORYS,SHOPS AND HOUSES.QUEENSBURYS ONE OF THE HIGHEST PLACES IN BRITIAN AS ITS 1000 FT HIGH.FARMERS MAINLY HAVE COWS,SHEEP AND OTHER KINDS OF ANIMALS.IN QUEENSBURY THERE ARE TWO MAIN ROADS AND TWO SIDE ROADS AND ONE SET OF TRAFFIC LIGHTS.THE HOUSES ARE MAINLY TERRACED AND MAINLY OLD PEOPLE LIVE IN THEM.THE OLD AND YOUNG LIVE IN QUEENSBURY FOR THE BRILLIANT VIEWS THERE IS ONLY ONE CHURCH IN THE HOLE OF QUEENSBURY THERE ARE A FEW FACTORYS AND THE REST IS FEILDS,HOUSES.
